details.purpose: To record the findings of urinalysis or dipstick testing

items.items: Semi-quantitative chemical analysis of a urine sample by direct observation. The color change occurring on each segment of a dipstick is read by being compared to a color chart.
Detection of blood in urine sample
Detection of ketones in urine sample
Detection of nitrites in urine sample
Detection of glucose in urine sample
Detection of urobilinogen in urine sample
Detection of Bilirubin in urine sample
Detection of white blood cells in the urine
Detection of protein in urine sample
Specific gravity is measuring the concentration of solutes in the urine relative to distilled water
The product or device used to measure the urine characteristics
